<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٦٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3909">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ مُرَّةَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنِ النَّذْرِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنَّهُ لَا يَرُدُّ شَيْئًا وَإِنَّمَا يُسْتَخْرَجُ بِهِ مِنَ الْبَخِيلِ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>